HasEffectivityReferences: has effectivity references, hence cannot be removed.
HasProductConfigurationsReferences: has product configurations, hence cannot be removed.
DetachFailedDueToCRDefined: Model cannot be detached because the reference has Configuration Revisions

CfgErrorInappropiateStateModelAttach: Model in inappropiate state cannot be attached
